                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipits of the texts; numbers of the
                           “tituli”; chapter numbers and the word mǝʿrāf; the letters ወ and ደ in the
                           genealogy of Christ (fols. 89va-90va); parts of the Canon tables;
                           elements of the quire marks and titles in the upper margin; elements of
                           the punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals.
 
 On the incipit
                           page of each Gospel and of Text I, a few lines are rubricated
                           (alternating with black lines).</seg>
